T1  - The Case of the Negative Nominal Interest Rates: New Estimates of the Term Structure of Interest Rates during the Great Depression
AU  - Cecchetti, Stephen G.
Y1  - 1988/12/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1086/261580
DO  - 10.1086/261580
T2  - Journal of Political Economy
JF  - Journal of Political Economy
SP  - 1111
